    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>flaked almonds </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden, then transfer to a <strong>food processor</strong> and reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
