    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then add to a colander and pour<strong> boiled water </strong>all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach </strong>under <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
