    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo and chicken are cooked, add the <strong>pea</strong> <strong>& basil pesto</strong> and <strong>remaining blanched peas</strong> to the pan</p><p>Stir it all together and cook for a final 1-2 min until everything is warmed through – this is your<strong> chicken & pea pesto orzo</strong></p>",
