      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken & pea pesto orzo</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>chilli oil</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the chilli oil!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
